{"tid":2343854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反正都係自毀長城，點解CCTVB唔去盡D？","createTime":"2020-12-28T08:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T05:17:45.000Z","uid":52764,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"39fe68b9c21463999131f7c6d2ea0ec083e7f909","tid":2343854,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:54:09.000Z","msg":"六七之後，左右兩派基本上無能力去威脅港英政府統治<br />\n但尚有生存空間<br />\n當中一樣野響我眼中係好爆<br />\n七十年代TVB曾經響星期日黃金時間播中共樣板戲《紅色娘子軍》<br />\n係咪左派影業買時間去播就不得而知<br />\n但係既然依家TVB都咁愛國，變左做CCTVB<br />\n不如玩大D，等班C9忠實觀眾唾棄啦<br />\n紅到咁仲唔夠愛國？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2pFGd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2pFGd3.jpg&h=33346d8f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n資料來源：1973年9月30日大公報第五版"},{"pid":"a6276a8382fc9831d83c09101db608f83e7b5698","tid":2343854,"uid":52764,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:54:43.000Z","msg":"《紅色娘子軍》@ 維基<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%BA%A2%E8%89%B2%E5%A8%98%E5%AD%90%E5%86%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%25BA%25A2%25E8%2589%25B2%25E5%25A8%2598%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%2586%259B&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=9abd5396\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%BA%A2%E8%89%B2%E5%A8%98%E5%AD%90%E5%86%9B</a>"},{"pid":"2b42c2cfa75282abfab2dc7db001bc44664fc5cc","tid":2343854,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:58:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69654f35ed000b7973640114332a7fcebd889111","tid":2343854,"uid":64953,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:59:27.000Z","msg":"又紅色娘子軍<br />\n又奇峯異洞<br />\n好淫賤"},{"pid":"2abac7873729246c86a26b1ae981355cf81d2f18","tid":2343854,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"69654f35ed000b7973640114332a7fcebd889111","tid":2343854,"uid":64953,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:59:27.000Z","msg":"又紅色娘子軍<br />\n又奇峯異洞<br />\n好淫賤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"另一套可以當獵奇咁睇，因為果陣時香港人除左返鄉下探親之外，好少會上大陸<br />\n叫CCTVB播紅色娘子軍啦"},{"pid":"98c702e91fcdb0787276c8afae05695d11227b65","tid":2343854,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:06:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8df42ccd3010e4c81c4f28844673028f37c5f66","tid":2343854,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:10:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64d4ce5191aff563cf50b0d7b4bb9cdd2138b6ca","tid":2343854,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f918c16a334c2ae998ff0ed506d82d10a6a88eb","tid":2343854,"uid":49916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NtPygTN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtPygTN.jpg&h=3c57e96d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15a3041e2634777256ce0bc723d0e2bf996c3344","tid":2343854,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6f918c16a334c2ae998ff0ed506d82d10a6a88eb","tid":2343854,"uid":49916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NtPygTN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtPygTN.jpg&h=3c57e96d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:24:28.000Z","msg":"播晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6364fa45c616b9ce98dfc76c557399dce52d5c75","tid":2343854,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T09:38:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cb174bbc73ddd3fd8c33f755523a1452d54ee1f","tid":2343854,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T10: